31
00:03:20,608 --> 00:03:21,608
Neeley!

32
00:03:26,808 --> 00:03:28,608
All right, pickers!

33
00:03:28,808 --> 00:03:29,408
Come on!

34
00:03:32,608 --> 00:03:35,608
Now look, stand on the same
side as him when he weighs

