00:03:35,808 --> 00:03:37,408
it so's he can reach it.

36
00:03:37,608 --> 00:03:40,008
And don't forget to stand there
after he pays you.

37
00:03:40,208 --> 00:03:43,008
You forgot that last time.
And a penny's a penny ain't it?

38
00:03:43,008 --> 00:03:45,808
Well, l guess l know what it is.
Well all right then.

39
00:03:50,008 --> 00:03:50,608
Three cents!

40
00:03:50,808 --> 00:03:52,208
Look, that stuff's worth more than
that!

41
00:03:52,408 --> 00:03:54,008
Shut up! l say what things are worth
around here!

42
00:03:55,208 --> 00:03:56,208
Who's next?

43
00:03:57,608 --> 00:04:00,008
Oh, hello little girl! Come on.

44
00:04:01,008 --> 00:04:02,408
Shut up! Shut up!

45
00:04:15,208 --> 00:04:23,808
You done fine.
Nine cents. Three, five, nine...

46
00:04:27,008 --> 00:04:30,408
There you are. An extra penny
because you're a nice little girl.

47
00:04:30,608 --> 00:04:34,008
