Burton: "Anatomy of Melancholy"

229
00:14:33,408 --> 00:14:37,408
Burton's "Anatomy of Melancholy"?
Are you sure you want this?

230
00:14:37,608 --> 00:14:38,408
Yes, ma'am.

231
00:14:38,608 --> 00:14:40,408
Don't you think is a trifle over
your head?

232
00:14:40,608 --> 00:14:41,208
Yes, ma'am.

233
00:14:41,408 --> 00:14:42,608
Then why did you select it?

234
00:14:42,808 --> 00:14:46,608
Well, l've read all the authors
beginning with "A",

235
00:14:46,808 --> 00:14:49,608
and all the "Bs" down to Burton.
ls next.

236
00:14:49,808 --> 00:14:52,608
You mean you're trying to read your
way straight through the library?

237
00:14:52,808 --> 00:14:54,008
Yes, ma'am.

238
00:14:54,208 --> 00:14:55,808
But, a book like this, you'll only
be confused.

239
00:14:56,008 --> 00:14:57,808
Please, l want to read clear through
the alphabet.

240
00:14:58,008 --> 00:14:59,808
l want to know everything in the
world.

241
00:15:01,008 --> 00:15:07,808
